[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 11    [0m:[38;5;9m[49m      2. (N13) Public vs private API Gateway: portal callers reach a public regional REST API; service-to-service callers should reach a private REST API exposed via a VPC interface endpoint. Two API Gateway deployments fronting the same recommender Lambda is a clean pattern.
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 12    [0m:[38;5;9m[49m      3. (A9) Per-patient throttling: WAF rate-limit on a header populated by the Lambda authorizer (resolved patient identifier). A starting point of 10 req/patient/min and 100 req/patient/hr protects shared backend quotas (Bedrock, OpenSearch) from a single misbehaving caller.
